overview: A&E Consulting specializes in contracted and permanent placement of cutting edge engineers. Our engineers are proficient in all developing languages (PHP, Java, Perl, ASP, C, C++, etc). Unlike other companies, we have privately held facilities located overseas which are controlled by our local San Francisco based project managers. This gives you the technical advantage over your competition to complete your projects accurately, on time and on budget without the high price of a local engineer.
